{"thag1.6:0.1":"Theragatha 1.6 ","thag1.6:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.6:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag1.6:0.4":"Sitavaniyattheragatha ","thag1.6:1.1":"“Yo sitavanam upaga bhikkhu, ","thag1.6:1.2":"Eko santusito samahitatto; ","thag1.6:1.3":"Vijitavi apetalomahamso, ","thag1.6:1.4":"Rakkham kayagatasatim dhitima”ti. ","thag1.6:1.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma sitavaniyo thero gatham abhasitthati. "}